*
 * GET /admin/products/{id}.xml
 *
 * Examples:
 *
 *      insales.getProduct({
 *        token: '1234567890',
 *        url: 'shop-test.myinsales.ru',

 *      }).then(response => {
 *        console.info(response.data);
 *      }).catch(err => {
 *        console.error(err);

 *          id: '12345',
